@startuml
title Program Loop - Level 1

skinparam ParticipantPadding 8

actor "User code" as User
participant "Sparkle" as Sparkle
participant "Window" as Window

User -> Sparkle : create application
User -> Sparkle : create window
User -> Sparkle : run()

loop until the program stops
	Sparkle -> Window : check messages
	Sparkle -> Window : update
	Sparkle -> Window : draw
end

Sparkle --> User : return exit code

note over Sparkle,Window
At the simplest level, Sparkle repeatedly
checks what happened, updates the program,
and draws the next image.
end note

@enduml
